Hello I had a brainwave idea for a server. I need help achieving this goal...There are a few coders out there who know me. Well...ive been coding for like almost a year now...and i still suck. But im trying. I will be doing most of my coding but i need some other coders who can help me and who can teach me. If you are interested in joining please fill out an application. You MIGHT be accepted. I only need a couple of good people right now. And if you put idk for any of them you wont be accepted.
[u]Coders[/u] -Syrilla -si force - - -
[u]Forums Maker and Etc.[/u] -magewolf -Aff -
[u]Idea peoplez[/u] -rs w00dcut -killer90210 -
[code] How do you want to help?:: How can you be a benefit?:: Why should i choose you over the other people?:: Your msn i can contact you by if your accepted:: [/code]
I just started this team yesterday...so i have a source to work with but nothing else. So no betas really for a while. But the forums will be made soon...Thank you again.
